latestIgtvVideos.title: a short clip from our "winning" western group song performance for ANUGOONJ

me and my girls won the zonals and r gonna perform in main University  at ANUGOONJ . be there to support us . we'll make a few changes and additions we are so ready for the finals at IP UNIVERSITY .  we sang our hearts out :p  maybe that's why we won it despite of tough competition out there . it definitely wasn't the best but definitely meant a lot to us bcs we prepared this in like a week  and  i directed a group for the first time .. it wouldn't have been possible without them girls standing behind me who got my back. 
catch us live at ANUGOONJ 2020 main fest. 
ps: also the crowd that cheered for us , thank you.😇🌼
